import { Form, Button } from 'semantic-ui-react' import {useFormik} from 'formik'; import * as Yup from 'yup'; export default function AdressForm() { const formik = useFormik({ initialValues: initialValues(), validationSchema: Yup.object(validationSchema()), }); return (
) } function initialValues(){ return { titile: "", name: "", adress: "", city: "", state: "", postalCode: "", phone: "" } }; function validationSchema() { return { title: Yup.string().required(true), name: Yup.string().required(true), adress: Yup.string().required(true), city: Yup.string().required(true), state: Yup.string().required(true), postalCode: Yup.string().required(true), phone: Yup.string().required(true), } };
